氣啦<br />\n根本香港大撚把人有錢買 樓又少過人<br />\n一日無公屋多 都唔撚會跌"},{"pid":"fb3ed64429b86513d3490d379a87a5ffd4dd84ab","tid":842214,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:38:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91bf0254f5b0ff22a85f446e168160e31c3b162b","tid":842214,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T07:42:19.000Z","msg":"幾年前德銀已經出黎話泡沫泡沫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有時都唔明d研究d專家係做乜撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 搞咁多analysis，不如回歸基本， 睇下demand and supply算啦<br />\n香港明明就好少supply"},{"pid":"c3bfa83ae3ff2b84113882e59909f2f85660023d","tid":842214,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T12:40:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/30/203406_f7940b77c31a05a00dbbaf7c260f39b8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F30%2F203406_f7940b77c31a05a00dbbaf7c260f39b8.png&h=06632a7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好脆弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}